{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "影與灰", "storyInfo": "“蕾繆安原諒你，莫斯提馬原諒你，伊萬傑利斯塔十一世原諒你，就算整個拉特蘭都原諒你——我也絕不原諒。”\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那是一個伊比利亞的小鎮，無論在地圖抑或史書，如今你找不到它的名字。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在還有人生活的時候，那裡叫做潮石鎮。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "潮石鎮的主教撫養了一名年幼的薩科塔。一個薩科塔......在這裡成長，在這裡學習，度過一生中最美好的歲月。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這裡樸素而貧瘠，但虔誠的生活原本不需要太多。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只是在大靜謐後的伊比利亞，人付出再多努力，生活永遠易碎。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一次瘟疫，一次饑荒，一次早有預謀的滲透，就足以擊垮一切。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為了拯救不是故鄉的故鄉，薩科塔來到聖城拉特蘭，請求一些微不足道的支援。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他得到的回答很簡單：你是我們的一員，他們不是。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "待薩科塔回歸伊比利亞，那個“故鄉”已然無存。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "甚至一切都被抹去，撫平，彷彿從未存在過。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "像一粒沙消失在沙漠裡，一滴水消融於浪潮中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "薩科塔經歷漫長的旅程，又回到拉特蘭，形銷骨立，宛若遊魂。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他往一座禮拜堂求訪獲封聖賢的主教，尋求解惑與引導。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "縱是聖賢，面對這許多質疑，也只能沉默。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他坐在長椅上，坐在那裡，從清晨到黃昏。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "菲亞梅塔，那就是我第一次見到安多恩。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，自掏腰包吧，這裡的維修費用很貴的。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下午茶的甜點往後只能減半了。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下！我聽到大教堂方向傳來戰鬥聲，您沒事吧！", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......？！是異端襲擊了您嗎？......這是我的失職！", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼緊張，保拉里奧，還記得上次大教堂掰腕比賽的冠軍是誰嗎？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是您。", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是稍微活動了一下手腕，不小心搞出了一點小意外而已。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城內的騷亂已經平息了。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，他們撤退了。我都還沒來得及炸爽——", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問可以進來嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，抱歉，教宗閣下，我失態了。", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是說，您要找的人已經到了。", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進吧，孩子們。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下，向您致敬......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下，您好，我是塞茜莉亞。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，歡迎，這裡有點亂。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝茶一般配什麼甜點？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......需要我做什麼？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，讓我想想......", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往自己的茶杯裡加塊方糖？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾，你得多加幾塊，糖分能舒緩緊張。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！好、好的......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下，如果我......想要離開拉特蘭，您會同意嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我不允許，你會服從嗎？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能不會。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就去吧。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......教宗閣下？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是個可憐的老頭子，最大的願望就是窩在軟乎乎的搖椅裡安度晚年，哪有功夫去管小女孩的旅行計畫呢？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可塞茜莉亞是......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是什麼？難不成她還能是天使和魔鬼的混血，讓啟示降臨的聖徒？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞只是個想要出門看看的小姑娘，對不對？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還帶著你媽媽的守護銃，是嗎？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對不起！我是不是應該交給艾澤爾哥哥......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，孩子。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獲得守護銃是一件莊嚴的事，原本得舉行隆重的儀式，需要監護人出席，導師的首肯，還有一大堆麻煩的文書工作......", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，你也沒到可以獲得守護銃的年紀。所以，悄悄地把它帶走吧。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的可以嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不敢說這是給你的禮物。每一把銃都是拉特蘭的寶貴財富。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，若只是孩子思念母親的寄託，我相信不會有人阻止。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶上它吧，孩子。你的身體狀況可能不允許你扣下扳機，幹掉什麼壞蛋......但它能提醒你，不管走到哪裡，你都是從拉特蘭出發。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯，謝謝您，閣下。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾，陪著她一起吧，算你的長期外勤任務。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得偶爾回來看看就行。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......真的有這個資格嗎？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當然有。你做出了選擇，不是嗎？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我會竭盡全力。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別讓塞茜莉亞被欺負了。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，去吧，時光可不等人。到了我這個年紀，就只會滿腦子想著睡午覺啦。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......教宗爺爺。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會一直走下去的。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是嗎。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將為你祝禱。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下，這就足夠了嗎？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和他們一起吃了點心，這就足夠了。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......按照您的指示，那個男人已經離開了。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不是應該多留他一會兒？也許吃塊巧克力能讓他打起點精神？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......教宗閣下，您太心軟了。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，薇爾麗芙，我們註定無法成為寒夜中的炬火。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，為抱薪者端上一杯熱茶......總還是做得到的。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這片大地難以容忍美善”......願那些不承認這一點的人能夠成功。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也該做下一件事了。騷亂已經平息，召集各國使節吧。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啟示既昭，我將行我須行。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我經常想起那一夜的事情。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "最初，不過是一個普通的清剿任務，一群普通的薩卡茲劫掠者。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們追尋他們留下的逃竄痕跡，找到了那個地方。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "詭異，但沒有任何敵意。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那些......被停滯在自己時間中的殘跡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我收到了那條臨時求援資訊......我離開了你們。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我離開了你們。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "求援的位置很近，來回最多不會超過半天。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我甚至提前趕回來了......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i16", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我記得腳下磚石的斑駁紋路，我記得冰涼雨水落在臉上的感覺。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我記得你黑色的角。也記得你緊閉的雙眼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "還有不知所蹤的安多恩。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只是......一次清剿任務而已。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只是一次清剿任務而已！！！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼事情會落到如此境地？到底哪一步做錯了？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果我沒有離開......如果我留在那裡，如果我和你們在一起，是不是這一切就不會發生？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "至少......至少不會......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "至少不是在我趕到的時候，一切都已經註定，什麼都無法挽回。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這感覺糟透了，說真的，糟透了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我唯一能做的，居然只是看著......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我本該和你們一起承擔。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g10_laterano_roof", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$batmeeting_intro", "key": "$batmeeting_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼想，菲亞梅塔，你不用承擔任何東西。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這是我的決定。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不管他那時正覬覦什麼力量，想探究什麼秘密，要得到什麼答案。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不管他的崇高理想，偉大事業，救贖了誰又引導了誰。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會原諒。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不為信仰，不為拉特蘭城，不為戍衛隊，甚至不為逝去的時光......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不原諒，只因為——", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，你辜負了信任你的人。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是你們。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......為什麼你還能安然無恙地出現在這裡？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼連教宗閣下都......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼......又有什麼為什麼......路從一開始就不存在，又能在虛無中尋得什麼？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的懺悔？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懺悔？不，我沒有懺悔......何方可供我懺悔？沒有光亮，沒有前途，受難者必將受難，悲哀者只有悲哀......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有得救，沒有樂園，這裡是拉特蘭，這裡只屬於我們......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果光芒本就是虛影......不，不是虛影......是實在......不如我們所願......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從未有過光芒......又何談照亮......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼，安多恩？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我放棄了嗎，我為什麼在這裡，我放棄了嗎？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這障壁如此之厚，我怎麼能夠擁抱他們？我怎麼可以擁抱他們？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許我只是個兜售虛假希望的騙子......騙到自己也信了這說辭......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白，我不明白。它的判斷是什麼？它想讓我去向何方？它的存在本身明明已經堵死了我的道路......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我向何處尋覓？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩！給我清醒一點！看清楚站在你面前的人是誰！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰......啊......菲亞梅塔......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又在發什麼瘋？！你那副振振有詞、理直氣壯的樣子呢？你的骨頭被抽走了嗎？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別讓我對一個癡人瘋漢興師問罪！看清楚你現在在哪裡！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我在拉特蘭，菲亞梅塔。我在大教堂之上。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很高興與你們重逢......不，我現在一點也不高興。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bullet_loading"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.7, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_originiumcast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這不是還會抵擋嗎？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還有臉抵擋？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說對不起。安多恩。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，跪下來，對莫斯提馬，還有蕾繆安的方向，說“對不起”！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是覺得自己沒有錯嗎？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的錯誤不可勝數。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你*拉特蘭俚語*還挺得意是不是？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不曾。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽著，安多恩，你有什麼信念，我不關心，你的信念全完蛋，我也不在意。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i13", "xScale": 0.9, "yScale": 0.9}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安原諒你，莫斯提馬原諒你，伊萬傑利斯塔十一世原諒你，就算整個拉特蘭都原諒你——我也絕不原諒。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我很抱歉，菲亞梅塔。", "name": "安多恩"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該道歉的人不是我。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當年的事，若再來一次......也許我仍會這麼做。", "name": "安多恩"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不是吧，認真的？你非要在菲亞梅塔面前這麼說？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且你現在不是......", "name": "莫斯提馬"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好。安多恩。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿出你的銃。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道，這不會有結果。", "name": "安多恩"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為我*拉特蘭俚語*是為了結果？！你以為我在這裡把你殺了，蕾繆安的八年就能回來嗎？！莫斯提馬的人生就能復原嗎？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*拉特蘭俚語*結果！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要找你算帳，是因為我*拉特蘭俚語*就是要找你算帳！懂了嗎？安多恩！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這是你的執念嗎，菲亞梅塔？", "name": "安多恩"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是又怎樣？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bullet_loading"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再說一遍，安多恩——拿出你的銃！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}